OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny remaining showers will soon
OL,6,Fclearing eastwards into the North Sea,
OL,7,Fleaving a very hot and humid day
OL,8,Facross England and Wales with strong
OL,9,Fsunshine. Hot across parts of Scotland
OL,10,Fand Northern Ireland with light winds
OL,11,Fand slightly cloudier skies.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely clear and settled
OL,14,Fwith light winds, with some mist and
OL,15,Ffog patches developing. It will remain
OL,16,Fwidely warm, particularly in the
OL,17,Fsouth, leading to a rather
OL,18,Funcomfortable night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
