OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FDry with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine, though an isolated shower is
OL,7,Fpossible in the west. Warm in the
OL,8,Fnorth, hot and humid elsewhere,
OL,9,Ffollowed by another very warm and
OL,10,Fmuggy night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
